Alpha Epsilon Delta (AED) is UW&ndash;Madison&rsquo;s Beta Chapter of the National Pre-Health Honor Society, bringing together students dedicated to service, scholarship, and the health professions
&nbsp;
At our general bi-weekly meetings, we have a variety of physician and pre-health speakers to advance you in your undergraduate career. We host volunteer events to help you get involved in the Madison community, Public Relations events to learn how to manage life as a pre-health student, and social events to enjoy a break from your busy schedule and spend time networking with other pre-health students!
