Delta Upsilon is more than just one big social club. Everyone in the chapter&nbsp;comes to have a good time, make life-long connections, and continue our traditions. Many members of Delta Upsilon have&nbsp;gone on to become leaders in school and in society. Alumni of our chapter include J.P. Morgridge (CEO Cisco Systems), Williams Davidson (Harley Davidson), William Kellett (CEO Kimberly Clark), and Brewster Shaw (Astronaut).

