VIVID Dance is a non-discriminatory K-Pop and Hip-Hop dance cover group. We seek passionate individuals interested in growing their artistic abilities through dancing, filming, and performing. VIVID uplifts all UW students by providing an inclusive platform for creative expression through dance, regardless of background, identity, or experience level. By welcoming individuals from these diverse cultural, social, and artistic backgrounds, we can showcase these differences through performance, fostering a sense of community and collaboration within the university.
Our group&rsquo;s emphasis on K-Pop and Hip-Hop allows members to explore different cultural forms of dance while embracing these unique perspectives. This supportive atmosphere helps students from all walks of life feel seen, valued, and empowered to explore their passions at the University of Wisconsin-Madison and beyond.&nbsp;
