The name of the organization shall be Women Impacting Supply Chain Excellence, also known as WISE, a student organization at the University of Wisconsin-Madison.&nbsp;
The purpose of our organization is to bring together University of Wisconsin-Madison students who are interested in or currently majoring in supply chain management, with the primary purpose of promoting the field of supply chain management logistics.&nbsp;
